select
r_r_tanggal as tanggal,
r_r_m_w_id as id_waroeng,
SUM(r_r_detail_reguler_price * r_r_detail_qty) AS nominal_refund
from "rekap_refund_detail" inner join "rekap_refund" on "r_r_id" = "r_r_detail_r_r_id" inner join "m_produk" on "m_produk_id" = "r_r_detail_m_produk_id" where "m_produk_m_jenis_produk_id" = '11' and "r_r_m_area_id" = '5' and "r_r_m_w_id" = '58' and "r_r_tanggal" = '2023-11-07' group by "tanggal", "id_waroeng"

select "r_t_m_area_nama" as "area", "r_t_m_w_nama" as "waroeng", "r_t_tanggal" as "tanggal", "r_t_m_w_id" as "id_waroeng", SUM(r_t_detail_reguler_price * r_t_detail_qty) AS nominal_wbd, SUM(CASE WHEN LENGTH(r_t_member_id) = 5 AND CAST(r_t_member_id AS bigint) < 103531 THEN (r_t_detail_reguler_price * r_t_detail_qty) ELSE 0 END) AS total_nominal_pegawai from "rekap_transaksi" left join "rekap_transaksi_detail" on "r_t_detail_r_t_id" = "r_t_id" left join "m_produk" on "r_t_detail_m_produk_id" = "m_produk_id" where "m_produk_m_jenis_produk_id" = '11' and "r_t_m_area_id" = '5' and "r_t_m_w_id" = '58' and "r_t_tanggal" = '2023-11-07' group by "tanggal", "area", "waroeng", "id_waroeng" order by "total_nominal_pegawai" desc
